{
  "stem": "17001.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 404.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of the [HUNGARIAN], they spoke Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't speak Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She started to say something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my sister took the knife and says if you open up your big filthy so-and-so mouth, I'm going to kill you before you have a chance to say boo.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she says, she's mashugana, she's mashugana.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said, oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She is mashugana.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You better listen to her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we sat there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We got the fifth one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were times when they selected us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were lucky we survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And each time when they selected is like 100 years fell off our shoulders.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was just getting to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a time when my younger sister got this rash.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when Mengele selected, she-- he wanted only skin-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] clean skin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No rash.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No blemish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No cuts.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Clean.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we had the lice eating us up, we would shove it off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wouldn't dare to scratch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As much as it hurt and much as it was itching, we wouldn't dare to scratch.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when my sister got this rash, there was-- I didn't even know about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she knew about it, that there was a place end of the lager where they had some kind of a ointment, and they put it in your body, that cleaned out the-- it's a infection that spreads like wildfire.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They call it [HUNGARIAN] in Hungary, But I don't know what's the name in English.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as we were standing Zahlappell, was hot like anything, and my sister Clara is throwing up only green saliva.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, I'm fainting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't stand the smell of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whoever it is, get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this and that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
